---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Chai & Coffee Catering Vancouver | Sula Café Catering for Offices & Events"
	description="Live chai bars, specialty coffee stations, and bakery catering in Vancouver. Perfect for offices, weddings, and private events. From Sula Café in East Vancouver."
	canonical="/cafe-catering"
	ogImage="https://sulacafe.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/sula-cafe-near-me-vancouver.webp"
>

	<Fragment slot="schema">
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org",
			"@type": "Service",
			"name": "Chai and Coffee Catering Vancouver",
			"provider": { "@id": "https://sulacatering.com/#organization" },
			"areaServed": ["Vancouver", "Burnaby", "Richmond", "Surrey", "North Vancouver"],
			"serviceType": "Café and Beverage Catering",
			"description": "Live chai stations, specialty coffee bars, and bakery catering from Sula Café — for offices, weddings, and private events in Vancouver."
		})} />
	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('https://sulacafe.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/sula-cafe-near-me-vancouver.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<p class="gold-label">Sula Café Catering</p>
			<h1>Chai, Coffee &<br/><em>Bakery Catering</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">Live chai stations, specialty coffee bars, and freshly baked goods — the perfect addition to any event.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Book a Café Catering</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">Where Flavour Meets Celebration</p>
				<h2>Fresh Brews, <em>Anywhere</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
				<p>Sula Café is the café and bakery extension of Sula Indian Restaurant. While Sula handles full Indian catering, the Café focuses on artisanal chai, specialty coffee, and freshly baked goods. Beautiful on its own, transcendent when paired with our full catering service.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="https://sulacafe.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/brunch-catering-vancouver-sula-cafe.webp" alt="Brunch catering Vancouver Sula Cafe" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<section class="section section-plum">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="alt-row">
				<div class="alt-row-img reveal-left">
					<img src="https://sulacafe.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/croissaint-near-me-vancouver-sula-cafe.webp" alt="Bakery catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="alt-row-content reveal-right">
					<p class="gold-label">Live Chai Stations</p>
					<h2>The Original <em>Comfort Drink</em></h2>
					<p>Authentic masala chai brewed fresh on-site by our team. Multiple flavours including kashmiri, ginger, cardamom, and saffron. The aroma alone transforms a room.</p>
					<p>Perfect for weddings, corporate breakfasts, and festive gatherings.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="alt-row reverse">
				<div class="alt-row-img reveal-right">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/cocktail-bar-vancouver.webp" alt="Specialty coffee bar Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="alt-row-content reveal-left">
					<p class="gold-label">Specialty Coffee Bars</p>
					<h2>Espresso, Lattes, <em>Cold Brew</em></h2>
					<p>Barista-staffed coffee stations for offices, conferences, and private events. From morning espresso to afternoon iced lattes — we keep your team caffeinated and inspired.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="alt-row">
				<div class="alt-row-img reveal-left">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/desserts-vancouver.webp" alt="Bakery platters Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="alt-row-content reveal-right">
					<p class="gold-label">Bakery Platters</p>
					<h2>Freshly Baked, <em>Beautifully Plated</em></h2>
					<p>Croissants, pastries, scones, and savoury baked snacks delivered fresh from our East Vancouver bakery. The perfect addition to office breakfasts, baby showers, and afternoon teas.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="alt-row reverse">
				<div class="alt-row-img reveal-right">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Mumbai-vada.webp" alt="Live street food stations Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="alt-row-content reveal-left">
					<p class="gold-label">Live Street Food</p>
					<h2>Pani Puri, Chaat, <em>Dosa</em></h2>
					<p>Pani puri, chaat, dosa, and samosa stations served live by our team. An interactive experience that turns any event into a celebration of Indian street food culture.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="image-banner" style="background-image: url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/masala-chai-sula-indian-restaurant.webp');">
		<div class="image-banner-content reveal">
			<h2>One Cup, <em>One Connection</em></h2>
			<p>Authentic masala chai, brewed by hand, served with warmth.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">Perfect For</p>
				<h2 style="font-size:42px;font-weight:400">Offices, Weddings, <em style="color:var(--gold)">Private Events</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
				<p style="font-size:17px;max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;color:rgba(50,34,28,0.8)">Whether it's a quick coffee break for your team, an afternoon tea setup for a private gathering, or a chai bar add-on for your wedding reception — we keep things warm, welcoming, and effortless.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<p class="gold-label" style="color:var(--gold-light)">Begin the Conversation</p>
			<h2>Add a <em>Café Bar</em> to Your Event</h2>
			<p>Tell us about your event. We'll respond within 24 hours with a custom menu and quote.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
